2014年7月25日，该片在[[北美洲|北美洲]]放映了3,595场。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/counts/chart/?yr=2014&wk=30&p=.htm |title=Theater Counts for Week 30 of 2014 |publisher=Boxofficemojo.com |date= |accessdate=2014-07-26 |archive-date=2014-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140727022420/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/counts/chart/?yr=2014&wk=30&p=.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>上映当日票房是1100万美元，首周票房是2900万美元，排行第二名，紧随《[[露西_(電影)|露西]]》。<ref name="Grover and Michaud">{{cite web|authors=Ronald Grover and Chris Michaud|title='Lucy,' 'Hercules' beat expectations at weekend box offices|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=27 July 2014|accessdate=28 July 2014|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/07/27/us-boxoffice-idUSKBN0FW0KR20140727|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006150656/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/07/27/us-boxoffice-idUSKBN0FW0KR20140727|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

